column5: Hey everyone, I got around to making a facebook page for the northern ontario anglers. Try and keep it to if you live in North Bay or further north or if you come up for fishing trips quite a bit! please like the page share photos,videos, schedule small tournaments and share it with your angling friends!  http://www.facebook.com/groups/346287305481969/?notif_t=group_r2j

Hey everybody, just a heads up that joined or is interested in joining, I turned it into a group instead of a page, sorry for the inconvenience.  http://www.facebook.com/groups/346287305481969/?notif_t=group_r2j  here is the new link I will accept the group join request as soon as possible.
